dcterms:description: A dataset of handwritten digits used for training various image processing systems. It consists of 60,000 training images and 10,000 testing images, each of size 28x28 pixels.
dcterms:title: MNIST

dcterms:description: A dataset of fashion items used for training image classification models. It contains 60,000 training images and 10,000 testing images, each of size 28x28 pixels, representing various clothing items.
dcterms:title: MNIST Fashion
